sub_title: Managing Partner at Russell Advocaten B.V.
summary:
As managing partner of Russell Advocaten, I advise national and international businesses on all facets of their day-to-day business operations. I have a broad range of specializations in questions regarding businesses, personnel, real estate and government. For more info: www.russell.nl/team/reinier-russell-lawyer
